OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Kieran
OL,8,FCarter
OL,10,FA new study by researchers in Finland
OL,11,Fsuggests that difficult video games
OL,12,Fcould have a positive impact on
OL,13,Fgamers' mental health.
OL,15,FThree academics from Aalto University
OL,16,Fanalysed how gamers playing the video
OL,17,Fgame "Dark Souls" interacted with each
OL,18,Fother and talked about their feelings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
