OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FThey observed how the challenging
OL,8,Fnature of the game "cultivated
OL,9,Fresilience and perseverance" in
OL,10,Fgamers' real lives, whilst the dark
OL,11,Fthemes and atmosphere encouraged
OL,12,Fpositive discussions about depression.
OL,14,FThe researchers also concluded the
OL,15,Fsupportive online communities built up
OL,16,Faround games like this led to positive
OL,17,Finteractions and impacts on players'
OL,18,Fmental health.
