OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FDark Souls is a critically acclaimed
OL,8,Fvideogame franchise made by Japanese
OL,9,Fgame developer FromSoftware. The dark
OL,10,Ffantasy action role playing game is
OL,11,Fknown among gamers for it's difficulty
OL,12,Fand bleak atmosphere.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, one of the
OL,15,Freport's authors, Jaakko Vakeva, said
OL,16,Fhe was surprised by how overtly
OL,17,Fplayers described connecting events in
OL,18,Fthe game to their real lives.
