OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,F"They would start applying what the
OL,8,Fgame had taught them to tackle their
OL,9,Fpersonal challenges... Cooperation in
OL,10,Fthe game inspired them to ask for help
OL,11,Fin the real world," Vakeva said.
OL,13,F"Our findings suggest that the
OL,14,Fextensively challenging yet rewarding
OL,15,Fnature of the gameplay, combined with
OL,16,Fits narrative context, could foster
OL,17,Fcoping skills, empowerment, and a
OL,18,Fsense of self-efficacy that extend far
OL,19,Fbeyond the gameplay."
