OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FPosting about the difficulty of these
OL,8,Fgames one user wrote: "You don't need
OL,9,Fto win each fight, but what matters is
OL,10,Fthat you persist and keep going
OL,11,Fdespite getting defeated, always
OL,12,Fstriving to improve. This mindset has
OL,13,Fbeen very helpful for me in dealing
OL,14,Fwith my own problems and not getting
OL,15,Foverwhelmed by them."
