OL,7,FAnother player described how the
OL,8,Fchallenging nature helped them in
OL,9,Fevery day situations writing that they
OL,10,Fplayed the game, "whenever I'm feeling
OL,11,Fmelancholic, or when I'm struggling
OL,12,Fwith a difficult period of my life".
OL,14,FThey added: "It gives me this feeling
OL,15,Fthat if I'm able to beat this, I'm
OL,16,Fable beat other things as well."
