OL,7,FVakeva added that finding such
OL,8,Fpositivity in a thematically dark game
OL,9,Fshouldn't necessarily be surprising.
OL,11,F"I don't think it's particularly
OL,12,Funusual, if you think of art and
OL,13,Fentertainment media more generally:
OL,14,Ffor instance, what it is that draws
OL,15,Fpeople towards watching some
OL,16,Femotionally challenging movie," Vakeva
OL,17,Fsaid.
