OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,F"After all, tragedy is an age-old
OL,8,Fgenre of drama that is associated with
OL,9,Fthis idea of catharsis, that is, a
OL,10,Fpurification of negative emotions by
OL,11,Fway of expressing or experiencing
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FIt's not the first time video games
OL,15,Fhave been linked to mental health.
OL,16,FDuring the pandemic many multiplayer
OL,17,Fgames became means of communication
OL,18,Ffor people isolated from physical
OL,19,Fconnection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
