OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FAnimal Crossing, a life simulation
OL,8,Fgame released by Nintendo during the
OL,9,Ffirst Covid lockdown, provided a
OL,10,Fmeeting place for friends and even saw
OL,11,Fcancelled graduation ceremonies,
OL,12,Fdates, and birthday parties recreated
OL,13,Fin the cheerful game world.
OL,15,FOxford academics found as well as
OL,16,Fproviding community and connection
OL,17,Fthere was a small correlation between
OL,18,Fmental wellbeing and the amount of
OL,19,Ftime spent playing the game.
