OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,F"Contrary to many fears that excessive
OL,8,Fplay time will lead to addiction and
OL,9,Fpoor mental health, we found a small
OL,10,Fpositive relation between game play
OL,11,Fand affective wellbeing," they wrote.
OL,13,FAdding: "Players who objectively
OL,14,Fplayed more in the past two weeks also
OL,15,Freported to experience higher well-
OL,16,Fbeing."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
