OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FOpen world games like Nintendo's
OL,8,FLegend of Zelda have also previously
OL,9,Fbeen linked to improved mental health,
OL,10,Fwith Researchers from Imperial College
OL,11,FLondon suggesting they "could be used
OL,12,Fas therapeutic tools for stress and
OL,13,Fanxiety management, offering a cost-
OL,14,Feffective and accessible method to
OL,15,Fimprove mental health".
