OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FSpeaking about the significance of
OL,8,Fresearch like this into video games
OL,9,Fand mental health they added: "The
OL,10,Ffinding that open-world games may
OL,11,Fenhance people's well-being through
OL,12,Fenhanced escapism and relaxation is
OL,13,Fnot trivial, given the growing
OL,14,Fevidence that other forms of
OL,15,Fentertainment, such as traditional
OL,16,Fsocial media, contribute to adolescent
OL,17,Fanxiety and depression."
