OL,3,CStuck in hard mode? Why tricky video
OL,4,Cgames could be good for your mental
OL,5,Chealth
OL,7,FDr Foldes added: "Greater attention
OL,8,Fshould be given to involving young
OL,9,Fpeople and clinicians early in the
OL,10,F(game) design process.
OL,12,F"Different types of games likely
OL,13,Fbenefit different people," Dr Foldes
OL,14,Fsaid, "but we currently lack
OL,15,Fsufficient understanding of exactly
OL,16,Fhow these differences manifest."
